</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="131" pageNumber="132" type="reference_group">
<paragraph pageId="131" pageNumber="132">
<taxonomicName authorityName="R. R. Mill" authorityYear="2009" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Convolvulaceae" genus="Seddera" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Seddera semhaensis" order="Solanales" pageId="131" pageNumber="132" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="semhaensis">Seddera semhaensis</taxonomicName>
R.R.Mill, Kew Bull. 64: 231. 2009. (Sebsebe et al. 2009: 231). Type. SOCOTRA, Semha Island, 
